	Label:
		markup: True
		text:'The username and password protect [color=00abae]all your passwords in Reminiscor.[/color]\n\nTo keep your data safe on your device we have set the default allowable username size to [color=00abae]eight characters[/color] and the password size to [color=00abae]ten characters.[/color]\nThe username cannot include a comma, remaining special characters are allowed.'
